  "title": "Procurement Coordinator (Supply Chain)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a <strong>Marine and Offshore Industry.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Procurement Coordinator to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West </strong>- easily accessible.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for the<strong> full spectrum of the purchasing process, including sourcing, quotation enquiries, price negotiation, order placement, and delivery coordination.</strong></li><li>Perform data entry and processing of Purchase Orders (POs).</li><li><strong>Maintain accurate records of procurement activities, i</strong>ncluding contracts, purchase orders, and supplier performance.</li><li>Ensure proper documentation and filing in compliance with ISO guidelines.</li><li>Develop and maintain strong relationships with suppliers, negotiate pricing and contract terms, and monitor supplier performance.</li><li>Source suppliers and procure electrical equipment, spare parts, and other electronic components.</li><li>Ensure timely delivery of materials and services.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business Administration, Supply Chain Management, or a related field.</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant experience.</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click </em><em><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></em><em> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</em><br /><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</em><br /><br /><em>Email Address: </em><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</em></a></p><p><em>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</em><br /><em>EA License No: 19C9682</em><br /><em>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</em></p>",
